  <brief_title>Study for Evaluating Life Quality in Patients With Rhinoconjunctivitis</brief_title>
  <acronym>ÍCARA</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective Study for Evaluating Life Quality and Its Determinant Factors as Treatment Adherence and Immunotherapy Satisfaction in Patients With Rhinoconjunctivitis With or Without Asthma, Sensitized at Least to One Aeroallergen</official_title>
  <sponsors>
