  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of ths study is to evaluate changes in life quality of patients affected by
      rhinoconjuntivitis with or without asthma after immunotherapy treatment. It is an
      observational, prospective and comparative study before-after immunotherapy treatment with a
      one year follow-up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
